Netflix Clone (HTML/CSS/JavaScript)

This project is a Netflix clone created using HTML, CSS, and some basic functionality of vanilla JavaScript. It aims to replicate the basic design and features of the Netflix web application.

Features:

-User registration and login
-Browse and search for movies and TV shows
-Display movie and TV show details
-Play movie trailers
-Add movies and TV shows to favorites
-Responsive design for various screen sizes

Contributing
Contributions to the Netflix clone are welcome! If you find any bugs or have suggestions for improvements, please open an issue or submit a pull request
